Use puppet to install the httpd package and start the httpd service.
Install the following into /var/www/html/index.html, the file should be
owned by apache and have mode 0644.
--
<html>
<head><title>LOPSA-East 2014</title></head>
Welcome to Puppet 101 at LOPSA-East 2014
--
* Note that /var/www/html will not exist until after the httpd package 
  has been installed.
  (hint: Trifecta)
